598
00:33:16,618 --> 00:33:19,118
A doctor-patient relationship?

599
00:33:19,153 --> 00:33:20,920
That's very unethical.

600
00:33:20,955 --> 00:33:24,390
- Yeah, it is.
- Very unethical.

601
00:33:24,426 --> 00:33:27,092
What was wrong with you, Ben?

