00:39:23,957 --> 00:39:27,223
She's trying to help people,
fight the good fight.

713
00:39:34,334 --> 00:39:36,760
I'm just a junkie
looking for a fix.

714
00:40:08,366 --> 00:40:10,366
<i>You've reached Louise Malick,
