00:41:24,204 --> 00:41:26,116
I don't want to stop.

738
00:41:27,907 --> 00:41:29,974
I think there's something
wrong with me.

739
00:41:30,009 --> 00:41:33,410
Well, I mean, yeah. Obviously.

